  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eThe thought of historic Philadelphia conjures up a mixture of vignettes from America’s collective memory including 19th century brownstones and post-industrial blocks as recent as the 1960s. \u003ca href=\"https://gnomearch.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGnome Architects\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e adds to that image bank with the design for their \u003ca href=\"https://gnomearch.com/projects/delancey-residence/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDelancy Residence\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, a contemporary work situated within a modernist neighborhood in close proximity to the waterfront Schuylkill River park and historic Fitler Square. Pulling from the local landscape, and with great respect for existing architectural vernacular, the firm creates new connective tissue between nature and neighborhood, present and past.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562784\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562784\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-10-dining-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A woman ascends the stairs in a modern living space, designed by Gnome Architects, featuring a dining area with a glass table, white chairs, large windows, and captivating wall art.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-10-dining-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-10-dining-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-10-dining-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-10-dining.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe property is steeped in tradition providing the bones from an original structure, which had suffered a major fire, for Gnome Architects to flesh out into an updated home in service of a young family – a solution that echoes a way of life lost to the average current new build. Using the surviving structure as a plinth, the challenge became finding ways to expand vertically while adhering to zoning constraints and avoiding ostentatious exterior finishes.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562781\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562781\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-07-dining-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"The modern dining room features a white table, six chairs, and a glass chandelier. A large window reveals the enchanting garden beyond. A blurred figure strolls by, while artwork and flowers grace the sideboard.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-07-dining-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-07-dining-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-07-dining-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-07-dining-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-07-dining.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562782\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562782\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"h