en-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-09-kitchen-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-09-kitchen-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-09-kitchen.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562778\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562778\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-04-living-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room features a beige sectional sofa, a patterned armchair, a flat-screen TV on a wooden built-in shelf, and a window offering a serene view of trees.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-04-living-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-04-living-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-04-living-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-04-living.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe addition creates a stacked box of interconnecting volumes stitched together by a skylit switchback staircase. The composition is informed by minimalist geometry that, together with the facade’s graphic language, must address a variety of contextual requirements: reconcile aesthetics with adjacent mid-century modern housing, preserve the existing entry courtyard and second floor street-facing terrace, and mitigate horizontal expansion through step-backs with additional floors. Passersby and neighbors alike can appreciate how the envelope’s original stucco and board-formed elements transition to a field of textured cement panels with generous glazing staggered as the windows ascend.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562779\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562779\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-05-living-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"In this modern living room you\u0026#39;ll find a beige sectional sofa, wall-mounted TV, and wooden shelves. A coffee table adorned with magazines and a plant adds flair. Light wood flooring and a large window ensure the space feels bright and airy.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-05-living-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-05-living-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-05-living-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-05-living.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEach space has its own unique character and enhances the connection between indoor and outdoor living, which is a priority for the residents. Upon arrival, guests are greeted by a privacy gate before a procession through the courtyard and into the foyer. The home comprises four livable floors atop a basement where the gym and media center are located. The first floor at ground level contains three bedrooms located in corners opposite the car port.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562780\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562780\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-06-play-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"