\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-03-entry-810x1134.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-03-entry-800x1120.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-03-entry-768x1075.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-03-entry-1097x1536.jpg 1097w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-03-entry.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562785\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562785\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-11-bed-detail-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"The bedroom scene features a charming tufted headboard, a side table adorned with a vase of yellow flowers, and a glass of water beside stacked books. A single hanging light fixture adds warmth above.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-11-bed-detail-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-11-bed-detail-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-11-bed-detail-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-11-bed-detail-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-11-bed-detail.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e“We were challenged by the homeowners with trying to fit all of those program pieces into this very tight box. they really trusted us to guide them along the way.” Deck adds. “Fitting a lot within a very tight box was the name of the game and they’ve given us a lot of praise for pulling off successfully.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562786\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562786\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-12-bed-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"The bedroom features a large bed, a wooden dresser, and a flat-screen TV on the wall. Two large windows offer views of the surrounding buildings.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-12-bed-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-12-bed-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-12-bed-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-12-bed.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562787\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562787\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-13-bath-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom featuring a wooden vanity, marble countertop, and a vase of flowers. A large window offers views of the city skyline, while a glass-enclosed shower stands elegantly to the right.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-13-bath-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-13-bath-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-13-bath-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Gnome-Architecture-Delancy-Residence-13-bath.jpg 1